#~ msgstr "Mio signore Kalenz, infine ti ho trovato!"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Chantal! Granddaughter! What are you doing here? You were not attacked, I "
#~ "hope."
#~ msgstr "Chantal! Nipote! Cosa ci fai qua? Non sei stata attaccata, spero."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "We were, but the enemy was vanquished. There are much more serious "
